207
00:11:43,642 --> 00:11:45,918
Benar! Seekor hamster!

208
00:11:45,942 --> 00:11:48,918
Yang artinya bahwa rumah orang bernama Tn. Chono

209
00:11:48,942 --> 00:11:53,418
